tags.description: A Coast Guard rifle range until 1973, this park offers baseball and soccer fields, basketball courts, tennis courts, a picnic shelter, a play area, restrooms, grills and picnic tables, and serves as a trail head for the North Ottawa Dunes Park.
tags.name: Coast Guard Park
tags.old_name: Grand Haven Coast Guard Rifle Range

tags.description: This property offers 593 acres of wooded dunes located just off the Lake Michigan shoreline and uniquely situated between state, county and city parks. Ten miles of hiking trails link North Ottawa Dunes to North Beach Park and PJ Hoffmaster State Park.
tags.name: North Ottawa Dunes County Park
